resources.string: Here is Basic Tutorial of App
First open the App and select your Section.
After Selecting A Section You can see That Which Section was Selected
Now You can Select Day and you will Be able To View Your That Day Lectures List

Here is The Most Powerful Auto Select Feather.By Clicking on the Auto Select Button You Will Be Automatically Transferred To Current Day Lectures List.Many Times We Do not Remember the Current Day.So for Making this App faster this feather is Added To This App
Here after Selecting a Day or By Auto Selecting Day You You will Come.Here You will be able to View Your all Lectures List of the Selected Day.
Here is another PowerFull Feature That is Auto HighLighted Ongoing Lectures.Current Time Lecture is Highlighted in sky Blue Color
By Tapping on Setting Icon You Can Access about App and Developer and Many other options
If You found any Bug or error in the App or You Have any information/Update about subject/Time contact us. We are Always Ready To help You.
For any changes in Timing and Lectures Developers are Not Responsible.Further Changes will be available in next update.
